{"comments":"Linked X/Y Position Input Component\n\nA compound input for 2D position values, with individual X and Y inputs\nthat can be optionally linked for proportional changes.\n\n## Visual Layout\n\n```\n┌───────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  X  ████ 250.0 ████   🔗   Y  ████ 150.0 ████  │\n└───────────────────────────────────────┘\n   └── X input ──┘    │     └── Y input ──┘\n                      │\n                 Link toggle\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Two scrubable number inputs for X and Y\n- Link toggle to maintain aspect ratio\n- Independent or proportional editing\n- Combined output for both values\n- Visual feedback when linked\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Component.Motion.Property.PositionXY as PositionXY\n\nHH.slot _position unit PositionXY.component\n  { x: 250.0\n  , y: 150.0\n  , linked: false\n  , xLabel: \"X\"\n  , yLabel: \"Y\"\n  , step: 1.0\n  , precision: 1\n  , disabled: false\n  }\n  HandlePositionChange\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"PositionXY component\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"m","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"constraintAnn":[],"constraintArgs":[{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"constraintClass":[["Effect","Aff","Class"],"MonadAff"],"constraintData":null,"constraintKindArgs":[]},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","Component"],"Component"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","PositionXY"],"Query"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","PositionXY"],"Input"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","PositionXY"],"Output"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},